profiles: Attaché DC - Organisation commune des marchés

messages.subject: Message 1
messages.message: Godfather ipsum dolor sit amet. I want your answer and the money by noon tomorrow. And one more thing. Don't you contact me again, ever. From now on, you deal with Turnbull. That's my family Kay, that's not me. I have a sentimental weakness for my children and I spoil them, as you can see. They talk when they should listen. It's not personal. It's business.

messages.subject: Message 2
messages.message: Michael, you never told me you knew Johnny Fontane! My father taught me many things here - he taught me in this room. He taught me: keep your friends close, but your enemies closer. I see you took the name of the town. What was your father's name? Only don't tell me you're innocent. Because it insults my intelligence and makes me very angry.

messages.subject: Message 3
messages.message: We're both part of the same hypocrisy, senator, but never think it applies to my family. Just when I thought I was out... they pull me back in. It's a Sicilian message. It means Luca Brasi sleeps with the fishes. Leave the gun. Take the cannoli. In Sicily, women are more dangerous than shotguns.

messages.subject: Message 4
messages.message: You can act like a man! Your enemies always get strong on what you leave behind. Do me this favor. I won't forget it. Ask your friends in the neighborhood about me. They'll tell you I know how to return a favor. I know it was you, Fredo. You broke my heart. You broke my heart! When they come... they come at what you love.

messages.subject: Message 5
messages.message: I'm gonna make him an offer he can't refuse. It's an old habit. I spent my whole life trying not to be careless. Women and children can afford to be careless, but not men. Is that why you slapped my brother around in public? Why do you hurt me, Michael? I've always been loyal to you. I am sorry. What happened to your father was business. I have much respect for your father. But your father, his thinking is old-fashioned. You must understand why I had to do that. Now let's work through where we go from here.

messages.subject: Message 6
messages.message: Fredo, you're my older brother, and I love you. But don't ever take sides with anyone against the Family again. Ever. Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful that you have invited me to your home on the wedding day of your daughter. And may their first child be a masculine child. I don't feel I have to wipe everybody out, Tom. Just my enemies. Don't you know that I would use all of my power to prevent something like that from happening? What's the matter with you, huh? What am I going to do? Am I going to make that baby an orphan before he's born?
